{"tid":2289852,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（唔知得唔得）突然發現左個6合彩發達大計","createTime":"2020-11-17T14:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T06:26:31.000Z","uid":49163,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c371a5eeb9bc47c463a872f95a86ac0c5a4af09a","tid":2289852,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"香港人咪好興夾買6仔既 一注10蚊半注就5蚊<br />\n只要搵人同你夾 有幾多夾幾多 但唔買 甘你就淨羊5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有100個人同你夾就會淨羊1000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會個個都中3個字架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTazvzp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTazvzp.png&h=5894bb04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放心中3個字機率得1/61 仲難過帶套有bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人會問萬一真係中頭獎甘點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甘唯有扮唔記得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ebd0bc833183e597234c7f6f84e165b3887506","tid":2289852,"uid":41368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"同13億人一人俾一蚊你都有13億一樣道理"},{"pid":"27814a0acf6c73a8c8cdc72fe0c09cf9af3acc72","tid":2289852,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33ebd0bc833183e597234c7f6f84e165b3887506","tid":2289852,"uid":41368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"同13億人一人俾一蚊你都有13億一樣道理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b82cb270afd595ac5ff049859dfd6cb01a46a62","tid":2289852,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b849bb28c4ebcbd11499837002ab4b7ae00310","tid":2289852,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"我有個買全部number 嘅formula<br />\n抽是旦6個字，當 1 2 3 4 5 6 第1注<br />\n之後 尾數 當下1注嘅第1個數字<br />\n即 6 x x x x a<br />\n下1注 就a x x x x b<br />\nB x x x x c...<br />\n直至抽完所有數<br />\n<br />\n據說，有4條數學家夾份買2年後中頭獎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://我就用ramdom.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E5%B0%B1%E7%94%A8ramdom.org&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM46tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=d4bd64de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我就用ramdom.org</a> 對3年嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n結果係。。。<br />\n<br />\n每年中好多細獎<br />\n3獎中過1次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你試驗吧<br />\n中咗話我知"},{"pid":"3feed0e51acee6e9dc37fd0a6586ba58d106d35d","tid":2289852,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V37Frfo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV37Frfo.jpg&h=ba86a6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啱啱用左10蚊，中左五獎"},{"pid":"8f961b89d7b633208bcdaf85184cbcd5558e4e2d","tid":2289852,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3feed0e51acee6e9dc37fd0a6586ba58d106d35d","tid":2289852,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V37Frfo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV37Frfo.jpg&h=ba86a6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啱啱用左10蚊，中左五獎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:41:06.000Z","msg":"中2個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460ee66367b77cbbbfdea52925f5c44594d4deac","tid":2289852,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3feed0e51acee6e9dc37fd0a6586ba58d106d35d","tid":2289852,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V37Frfo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg